{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260419193544","title":"Agent eksplorasi codebase harus struktural, bukan sekadar search random","desc":"AI agent perlu dipandu untuk memahami struktur sistem, relasi modul, dan alur domain agar perubahan tidak hanya benar secara lokal.","tags":["permanent-note","governance","ai","agent"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"5a921f13e25119184e9d876792b49bb5","updated":1776603918145,"created":1776603918145,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","id":"zettel.20260419193544","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","id":"zettel.20260419193544","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.governance","alias":"governance","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.governance"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","id":"zettel.20260419193544","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.ai","alias":"ai","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.ai"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","id":"zettel.20260419193544","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.agent","alias":"agent","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.agent"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419193544","id":"zettel.20260419193544","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":18,"offset":758},"end":{"line":16,"column":63,"offset":803},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":3,"offset":1605},"end":{"line":28,"column":28,"offset":1630},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419193544"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419192952","id":"zettel.20260419192952","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1181},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1206},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419193544"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","id":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":3,"offset":4968},"end":{"line":104,"column":28,"offset":4993},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419193544"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"agent-eksplorasi-codebase-harus-struktural-bukan-sekadar-search-random\">Agent eksplorasi codebase harus struktural, bukan sekadar search random<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#agent-eksplorasi-codebase-harus-struktural-bukan-sekadar-search-random\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Agent eksplorasi codebase yang efektif harus memahami struktur sistem, file penting, relasi modul, dan alur domain, bukan sekadar mencari potongan kode secara acak.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Eksplorasi terstruktur memberi agent konteks sistemik yang lebih besar.</li>\n<li>Search random sering menghasilkan solusi lokal yang sintaksnya benar tetapi arsitekturalnya salah.</li>\n<li>Agent perlu diberi instruksi eksplisit untuk melakukan eksplorasi sebelum mengubah kode.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Instruksi agent sebaiknya memuat tujuan eksplorasi dan area penting yang harus dieksplorasi.</li>\n<li>Eksplorasi terstruktur juga membantu agent menghasilkan rekomendasi yang lebih konsisten.</li>\n<li>Ini menambah lapisan governance di atas kemampuan AI, bukan hanya menambah konteks repo.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>→ Dikuatkan oleh <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards\">Encoding Team Standards — executable AI instruction untuk konsistensi tim</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">governance (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">agent (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten (vault)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260419192952\">Plan, onboarding, dan tracker adalah artefak governance AI, bukan dokumentasi pasif (vault)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards\">Encoding Team Standards — executable AI instruction untuk konsistensi tim (vault)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel","t58wEmhAtf1GlHmO","suui91xeqz9oleqbmefavfl","2mtiit3qbzjx3fps6j2lrvl","3d3j63sy6aifg2cqmrty2j4","91eqybfohputr1iaxqbsbfe","xfsiepyapo4o9u17mvwwmmz","7udjlx2925dhyxgkrntgcbz","x1aw4xgjnlqqzeww7dkz75g","uq0494ev4mdkmc2k7tantoa","cjzzncwhf8qpuaoz764uzfn","y8jzdhjhhmqub1t9wx5w9e4","ff8zp75qbznut6joziqr1nx"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"},{"fsPath":"templates","seed":"dendron.templates","name":"dendron.templates","visibility":"private"},{"fsPath":"vault2","name":"vault-private","sync":"sync","visibility":"private","remote":{"type":"git","url":"git@github.com:zeihanaulia/journal.git"}}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateForma